PN,39102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1775758264
OL,3,C'Calculating' child abuser used Roblox
OL,4,Cto find schoolgirl victim 220 miles
OL,5,Caway
OL,7,FCarlo Tritta, 19, began talking to the
OL,8,Fteenager, who had played Roblox since
OL,9,Fshe was seven-years-old, on the app in
OL,10,FSeptember 2024 and later moved to
OL,11,Fother messaging services as he groomed
OL,12,Fher.
OL,14,FThe girl's mother said she uncovered
OL,15,Fthe abuse on her daughter's phone in
OL,16,FAugust 2025 when she became depressed.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/17
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
