OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1775758264
OL,3,C'Calculating' child abuser used Roblox
OL,4,Cto find schoolgirl victim 220 miles
OL,5,Caway
OL,7,FHe sent the schoolgirl, from
OL,8,FManchester, an old phone in an attempt
OL,9,Fto stop the abuse being uncovered and
OL,10,Fwent on to carry out "rampage of
OL,11,Fstalking", she added.
OL,13,FPolice revealed that, even after they
OL,14,Flaunched an investigation, Tritta sent
OL,15,Fher gifts and Moonpig cards.
OL,17,FOne printed message read: "I know your
OL,18,Fmum saw the last one but you need to
OL,19,Fseriously think about this and if she
OL,20,Fsees this you need to think about this
OL,21,Ftoo.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/17
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1775758264
OL,3,C'Calculating' child abuser used Roblox
OL,4,Cto find schoolgirl victim 220 miles
OL,5,Caway
OL,7,FHe added: "If this goes to court, this
OL,8,Fwill likely end up on the news, that's
OL,9,Fboth of our names ran through dirt for
OL,10,Fthe whole world to see," before
OL,11,Fsigning off "I love you, C x"
OL,13,FRoblox, which is the most frequently
OL,14,Fplayed game in the UK for eight to 12
OL,15,Fyear olds, said safety is its "top
OL,16,Fpriority".
OL,18,FBut the girl's mother told ITV News:
OL,19,F"I just never thought anything of this
OL,20,Fgame. It's a kid's game as far as I'm
OL,21,Faware.
OL,26,@rD@XO]sD@MOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/17
