PN,39105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1775758264
OL,3,C'Calculating' child abuser used Roblox
OL,4,Cto find schoolgirl victim 220 miles
OL,5,Caway
OL,7,F"Some parents think their child's
OL,8,Fplaying it, they're online playing
OL,9,Fwith their friends.
OL,11,F"But what you need to realise is
OL,12,Fthere's also people... who are a lot
OL,13,Folder, who are on that game for one
OL,14,Freason, and it's to groom.
OL,16,F"If you asked me months ago, would I
OL,17,Fthink something like this would
OL,18,Fhappen? No, not to my child."
OL,20,FDet Supt Rod Kenny praised the girl
OL,21,Ffor her bravery in pursuing the case
OL,26,@xD@AOU
