PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1775758264
OL,3,C'Calculating' child abuser used Roblox
OL,4,Cto find schoolgirl victim 220 miles
OL,5,Caway
OL,7,FCarlo Tritta was charged with a number
OL,8,Fof child sex offences and witness
OL,9,Fintimidation following an
OL,10,Finvestigation by police in Hampshire.
OL,12,FHe was jailed for 28 months, and put
OL,13,Fon the sex offenders register for 10
OL,14,Fyears, after pleading guilty to sexual
OL,15,Fcommunication with child, causing a
OL,16,Fchild to watch a sexual act, making
OL,17,Findecent images. He also admitted two
OL,18,Fcounts of witness intimidation and
OL,19,Fcriminal damage.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/17
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
