PN,39107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1775758264
OL,3,C'Calculating' child abuser used Roblox
OL,4,Cto find schoolgirl victim 220 miles
OL,5,Caway
OL,7,FDetectives said the 19-year-old, of
OL,8,FWest Drive, Bishopstoke, tried to
OL,9,Fdrive a wedge between the girl and her
OL,10,Fmother.
OL,12,FThe mum said she bought security
OL,13,Fcameras for their home because she
OL,14,F"thought he was going to do something
OL,15,Fto me."
OL,17,FHowever, he travelled the 200 miles
OL,18,Ffrom his Eastleigh home to the girl's
OL,19,Fhouse in Greater Manchester three
OL,20,Ftimes while he was on bail and wearing
OL,21,Fa GPS tracker.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/17
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
