PN,39108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1775758264
OL,3,C'Calculating' child abuser used Roblox
OL,4,Cto find schoolgirl victim 220 miles
OL,5,Caway
OL,7,FOn one occasion he took a camera off
OL,8,Fthe back door and put it in kitchen
OL,9,Fsink in an attempt to destroy it, the
OL,10,Fgirl's mother said.
OL,12,FCarlo Tritta answered 'yes' when he
OL,13,Fwas arrested by police on allegations
OL,14,Fof child sexual abuse
OL,16,FPolice said Tritta persuaded the girl
OL,17,Fto share indecent images of herself.
OL,19,FThe mother added: "My daughter was
OL,20,Fbacked into - not a corner - but she
OL,21,Fjust didn't know a way out.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/17
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
