CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1775758264
OL,3,C'Calculating' child abuser used Roblox
OL,4,Cto find schoolgirl victim 220 miles
OL,5,Caway
OL,7,FDC Jodi Bartlett, who investigated the
OL,8,Fcase at Hampshire Constabulary, said:
OL,9,F"Tritta's behaviour lays bare the
OL,10,Fterrifying realities of how criminals
OL,11,Fuse the online world to target and
OL,12,Fharm vulnerable people. Do you truly
OL,13,Fknow who you, or your child, is
OL,14,Fspeaking to online?
OL,16,F"The victim in this case was just 14-
OL,17,Fyears-old. She and her mother were
OL,18,Fsubjected to a campaign of fear and
OL,19,Fabuse at the hands of obsessive and
OL,20,Fpredatory Tritta.
OL,26,@qD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/17
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
