FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1775758264
OL,3,C'Calculating' child abuser used Roblox
OL,4,Cto find schoolgirl victim 220 miles
OL,5,Caway
OL,7,F"Gaming platforms should be spaces
OL,8,Fwhere people, especially children, are
OL,9,Fsafe. The anonymity of the internet
OL,10,Fallows dangerous individuals like
OL,11,FTritta to prey on others for their own
OL,12,Ftwisted gain, and the lengths that
OL,13,FTritta went to in order to maintain
OL,14,Fhis abuse of this young girl is
OL,15,Fshocking."
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/17
