CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1775758264
OL,3,C'Calculating' child abuser used Roblox
OL,4,Cto find schoolgirl victim 220 miles
OL,5,Caway
OL,7,FDetective Superintendent Rod Kenny,
OL,8,Fwho heads of the child abuse and
OL,9,Fsafeguarding department added: "Once
OL,10,Fthe victim had shared a nude image of
OL,11,Fthemselves, the offender had a control
OL,12,Fand a hold over them and that control
OL,13,Fand hold over them continued through
OL,14,Fthe course of their online
OL,15,Frelationship.
OL,26,@qD@`OU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/17
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
