PN,39113
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1775758264
OL,3,C'Calculating' child abuser used Roblox
OL,4,Cto find schoolgirl victim 220 miles
OL,5,Caway
OL,7,F"And it was only when the mother
OL,8,Fdiscovered the concerns that she was
OL,9,Fable to reassure her daughter that she
OL,10,Fwasn't in trouble, that this was about
OL,11,Fhis offending behaviour and not the
OL,12,Factions she taken.
OL,14,F"It's really important that your
OL,15,Fchildren and young people understand
OL,16,Fthat... there are people out there
OL,17,Fthat can help you in that. You don't
OL,18,Fhave to let offenders control you."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/17
