OL,3,C'Calculating' child abuser used Roblox
OL,4,Cto find schoolgirl victim 220 miles
OL,5,Caway
OL,7,FPolice have encouraged potential
OL,8,Fvictims of child abuse to talk to an
OL,9,Fadult
OL,11,FA spokesperson for Roblox said:
OL,12,F"Safety is a top priority at Roblox.
OL,13,FOur policies firmly prohibit any kind
OL,14,Fof child exploitation and our systems
OL,15,Fare designed to limit chat for younger
OL,16,Fusers, block the sharing of personal
OL,17,Finformation and prohibit the sharing
OL,18,Fof external images and videos via chat
OL,19,F- some of the most prevalent avenues
OL,20,Ffor online harm.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G14/17
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
