FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39116
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1775758264
OL,3,C'Calculating' child abuser used Roblox
OL,4,Cto find schoolgirl victim 220 miles
OL,5,Caway
OL,7,F"We are always looking to continuously
OL,8,Fimprove and strengthen our
OL,9,Fprotections. Last week, Roblox became
OL,10,Fthe first gaming platform to require
OL,11,Fall users to go through age checks in
OL,12,Forder to communicate on our platform,
OL,13,Flimiting communications to people of
OL,14,Fsimilar ages, or those they already
OL,15,Fknow.
OL,17,F"While no system (including Roblox) is
OL,18,Fperfect, we do our best to detect,
OL,19,Fmoderate, and respond to reports about
OL,20,Fpeople and content that violate our
OL,21,FCommunity Standards.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G16/17
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
