OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39117
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1775758264
OL,3,C'Calculating' child abuser used Roblox
OL,4,Cto find schoolgirl victim 220 miles
OL,5,Caway
OL,7,F"We cannot prevent all bad actors and
OL,8,Fobjectionable content from appearing
OL,9,Fon Roblox, so we strongly encourage
OL,10,Fparents to talk to their kids about
OL,11,Finternet safety and to understand what
OL,12,Ftheir kids are doing online. This
OL,13,Fincludes discussing subjects like
OL,14,Fonline grooming."
OL,16,FPolice say any parents worried about
OL,17,Fonline safety visit the Internet Watch
OL,18,FFoundation website.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G17/17
